                           <locus target="#179ra">f. 179ra</locus>
                           <desc>b: Donation note. </desc>
                           <quote xml:lang="gez">
                              <locus target="#179ra">179ra</locus>b: ዝመጽሐፍ፡ ዘልጅ፡ ተወልደ፡ መድኅን፡ ዘወሀቦ፡
                              ለንኅብ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ሚካኤል፡ ስመ፡ አቡሁ፡ ወልደ፡ ማርያም፡ ...</quote>
                           <quote xml:lang="en"/>
                           <note> The Ms. was donated by lǝğ Tawalda Madḫǝn to the Church of Qǝddus
                              Mikāʾel, other family members are also mentioned. </note>
                        </item>
